    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I did the first releases of instantsearch.js, we have:\n- up to date project on github, default branch is now master\n- https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js\n- online demo (updated at release or manually with npm run gh-pages): http://algolia.github.io/instantsearch.js/\n- npm published (readme will be updated next release): https://www.npmjs.com/package/instantsearch.js\n- published on jsdelivr: http://www.jsdelivr.com/projects/instantsearch.js with automatic update through npm\n- no dist/ in github\n- dist/ is in npm\n- default export is dist/instantsearch.js in package.json\n- single release command: npm run release hope you love it\n- reproducible builds through npm-shrinkwrap.json\n- version is now in instantsearch.version\n- some badges and readme update\n",
